<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: starflight basics -->
  <ShipBasics.label>基礎星艦</ShipBasics.label>
  <!-- EN: Construct the structural and supportive elements of a starship. This is the first step in building a ship to leave this star system. -->
  <ShipBasics.description>建造星艦的基本結構，這是逃離這個星球的第一步。</ShipBasics.description>
  <!-- EN: Escaping from this planet - it would be freedom at last, and maybe a return home.\n\nBut also incredibly dangerous.\n\nA new Ship category is available in the Architect menu from which you may build ship parts once the appropriate technology is researched. Ships require several different parts in order to launch, including a ship reactor.\n\nShip reactors take 15 days to charge up and many desperate souls want off this planet. Once you begin that process, the ship reactor will emit an energy signature detectable from thousands of kilometers away. Raiders will flock to attack you in waves, with an intensity you've never seen. Mechanoids are also known to be attracted to such energy signatures.\n\nIt won't start until you activate your ship's reactor, but when it does, it'll be ferocious. You'll need to stockpile resources, weapons, and defenses for the onslaught if you hope to escape alive. -->
  <ShipBasics.discoveredLetterText>逃離這顆星球——終於獲得自由，或許有機會回到家鄉。\n\n但也可能伴隨著危險。\n\n在建築選單中新出現了一個星艦介面，你可以在此通過研究相關科技後建造星艦部件。星艦需要數個不同的部件才能起飛，當中包括星艦反應爐。\n\n星艦充能需花15天，然而許多絕望的靈魂盼望著離開這顆星球。一旦你開始程序，星艦反應爐會散發出可在數千公里外被偵測到的訊號。襲擊者會蜂擁而來，展開前所未見的進攻。機械軍團也會被吸引而來。\n\n這場史詩戰役在你啟動反應爐後才會發生。如果你希望能活著離開，你需要儲備資源、武器，來防衛猛烈攻擊。</ShipBasics.discoveredLetterText>
  <!-- EN: About: Launching the ship -->
  <ShipBasics.discoveredLetterTitle>關於︰星艦起飛</ShipBasics.discoveredLetterTitle>
  
  <!-- EN: machine persuasion -->
  <ShipComputerCore.label>機械核心</ShipComputerCore.label>
  <!-- EN: Build a reward-signal system to persuade an existing persona core into serving as a ship's machine captain. Since people sleep during interstellar travel, a persona core is necessary to handle the complex decisions of a years-long starflight. -->
  <ShipComputerCore.description>建造擁有神經機動系統的機械核心作為星艦艦長。由於人們在長達數萬年的星際旅行時需要休眠，因此必須要由機械核心來打理好一切事物。</ShipComputerCore.description>
  
  <!-- EN: vacuum cryptosleep casket -->
  <ShipCryptosleep.label>真空休眠艙</ShipCryptosleep.label>
  <!-- EN: Construct hardened cryptosleep caskets tough enough to be exposed to vacuum, for transporting people on the years-long journey between stars. -->
  <ShipCryptosleep.description>建造足以承受真空環境的休眠艙。用來搭載人們度過多年的星際旅行。</ShipCryptosleep.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Johnson-Tanaka drive -->
  <ShipEngine.label>JT推進器</ShipEngine.label>
  <!-- EN: Construct a Johnson-Tanaka drive for a ship. The JT drive can push you to other stars by leveraging quantum scale effects to beam momentum to distant stars. Of course, as with all starships, it still takes many years to get anywhere. -->
  <ShipEngine.description>建造一個名為Johnson-Tanaka的驅動裝置，JT可以利用量子比例效應，將光束能量射到遙遠的恆星，引導你到其他恆星。當然，跟其他星艦一樣，需花很多年才能到達你想要的地方。</ShipEngine.description>
  
  <!-- EN: starship reactor -->
  <ShipReactor.label>星艦反應爐</ShipReactor.label>
  <!-- EN: Build a long-duration nuclear reactor to power a starship. Note that reactors have a long startup process that will attract raiders. -->
  <ShipReactor.description>建造能為星艦長期提供動力的反應爐。請注意，反應爐的啟動過程很長，將會引來不速之客。</ShipReactor.description>
  
  <!-- EN: starflight sensors -->
  <ShipSensorCluster.label>星艦感測器</ShipSensorCluster.label>
  <!-- EN: Construct long-range sensors for a starship. These sensors are essential for navigation, communication, and threat avoidance. -->
  <ShipSensorCluster.description>建造星艦的長程感測器，這對於星艦的導航、通信、遠離威脅相當重要。</ShipSensorCluster.description>
  
</LanguageData>